{"tid":2144690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國公布制裁香港及中央官員　葉劉淑儀感憤怒","createTime":"2020-08-07T17:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T17:20:23.000Z","uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"01dd992f9ad8170416d3a4fb2f18977b244f13c0","tid":2144690,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1542492_1_20200808001330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1542492_1_20200808001330.jpg&h=a6c9bf7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國財政部公布制裁行政長官林鄭月娥、律政司司長鄭若驊、香港中聯辦主任駱惠寧等官員，指他們涉及打壓香港的自由。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀表示非常憤怒，批評美國「橫蠻無理」，粗暴干預香港內政，相信很多港人都會感到憤怒，她強調本港依法辦事，亦有責任維護國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀認為，美國受到某些人士遊說，「唱衰香港」，如前港督彭定康、立法會前議員羅冠聰等人，尤其美國總統大選即將來臨，有關人士在英美曝光，西方傳媒會當成他們維護香港人權，結果最終扭曲真相。<br />\n<br />\n她相信，北京當局會有反制措施，但目前難以推測，又認為中美角力，美國視香港為棋子，透過打壓香港以對中國施加壓力。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542492-20200808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542492-20200808.htm&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6CLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=bd7b5797\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542492-20200808.htm&h=c19f0a0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542492-20200808.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cce1575ed6fcfc5221056fc4ee3232c550e69d75","tid":2144690,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:13:44.000Z","msg":"除咗制裁，今日係梓樂離開9個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144688</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccyVKr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccyVKr4.png&h=fbc64625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c42c93c8c28cf8b188fa4280cc23bcbc6c284c1","tid":2144690,"uid":225684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"香港人感到極度興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb57451f690cdd70b1bf585c046ed8ea824b622e","tid":2144690,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"依個人相當有嚴疑<br />\n制裁冇佢份<br />\n所羅門又叫佢 Best Friend<br />\n仲唔係 25仔？"},{"pid":"dc397cc5e2885699f7b2b828b3b3a10643d32375","tid":2144690,"uid":3786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"普遍香港人極度憤怒點解冇佢份"},{"pid":"32ebe35ddb906eae2b07547fd79437294e19c722","tid":2144690,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/40DeeKa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40DeeKa.jpg&h=8513d666&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}